      <p>Martial arts schools all look similar on the surface — similar programs, similar pricing, similar photos. The differentiator is the culture and the instructor. A parent reading "my son has transformed — more confident, more focused, and genuinely excited to go to class" knows more than any website copy can tell them.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">Without social proof, you're competing on price and proximity. With it, you compete on outcomes — and that's a battle you can win.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">The testimonials that enroll martial arts students</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
