        <li><strong>Welcoming environment:</strong> "I was nervous as a complete beginner. Everyone was patient and supportive. Never felt out of place."</li>
        <li><strong>Instructor quality:</strong> "Sifu Chen explains technique so clearly. You understand the why behind every movement."</li>
        <li><strong>Fitness results:</strong> "Lost 20 lbs and gained muscle I didn't know I had. The workouts are intense in the best way."</li>
        <li><strong>Self-defense confidence:</strong> "I'm a woman who commutes alone. After a year here, I feel genuinely capable of protecting myself."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof works for martial arts schools</h2>
